===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Roxie (Masters)}}
Roxie forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Whirlipede}}, and its evolved form {{p|Scolipede}}, along with {{form|Toxtricity|Amped Form}} {{p|Toxtricity}} and {{p|Garbodor}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Her Toxtricity is capable of [[Gigantamax]]ing. Roxie has been a playable sync pair since the game's release.

Roxie has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]].

